		<h1 class="title">超级碗这个“美国春晚”今年都有什么亮点？</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/8/small/8.jpg?1448336190" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">马宁忆 金一雷</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-01-25 10:39:49 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
		<img src="/system/articles/longshows/5532/medium/5532.jpg?1422109590" alt="" />
